Definition: the act of persisting or persevering
Example: continuing or repeating behavior; his perseveration continued to the point where it was no longer appropriate
Synonyms: verb, change, persevere, persistence, persist, perseveration, communication, perseverate, continuance, the, act, of, persisting, or, persevering, continuing, repeating, behavior, his, continued, to, point, where, it, was, no, longer, appropriate
Category: noun.act
